STATE

Thomas W. MCNEILL 352P17-1 Supreme Court of North Carolina. December 7, 2017 Daniel P. O'Brien, Special Deputy Attorney General, Vernon K. Stewart, District Attorney, for State of North Carolina. Thomas W. McNeill, for McNeill, Thomas Wayne.
